Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:08.40,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,So there you are... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:12.40,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's where... you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.16,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,And that's... whose body you're using.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:21.04,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I got tired and could \Nfeel my soul being sucked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:26.36,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,you said you had to go because \Nthings were going south...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:28.15,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:31.99,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're there, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:35.47,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to win for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:39.79,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.24,JoJo-main,Dopp,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:46.30,JoJo-main,Dopp,0000,0000,0000,,Could you... call me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:49.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,like you always have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.25,JoJo-main,Dopp,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:04.06,sign_4099_21_No_one_can_escap,Op subs,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape the fate that was chosen for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:09.48,sign_4099_21_No_one_can_escap,Op subs,0000,0000,0000,,All that remains is the end, where you will all perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.53,sign_4099_21_No_one_can_escap,Op subs,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal greatness exists only within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:20.11,sign_4099_21_No_one_can_escap,Op subs,0000,0000,0000,,Sing a song of sorrow in a world where time has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:54.48,JoJo-EpTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(652,515)}Episodio 36 Diavolo Surfaces
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:58.33,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mista! Hurry up and pierce \Nyour Stand with this arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:01.36,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? \NRequiem's suddenly heading toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.20,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno! Stop Requiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.66,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! It's too far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.07,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H62CCF0&\4c&H701B62&}Crack
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.09,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.17,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,My gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.72,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Mista?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.13,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're touching the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.75,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Why is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.38,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of it, Mr. Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.26,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:29.75,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Glad I took that cop's Beretta just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.16,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,But what the hell, Bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.77,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd my revolver break all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.30,JoJo-main,Five,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe the boss got close?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.77,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass! Think before \Nyou talk, Number Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:47.58,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you saw someone coming \Nclose to us in this big, open space?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.00,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't see anyone at the \Nmoment the revolver broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.59,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,It's metal fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he's been overusing the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.49,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,The axis of the cylinder broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:00.59,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had a chance to do\Nany maintenance or inspections!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.42,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:16.28,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this thing's problem? \NIt's heading toward m-me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.84,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mista. It's heading towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.86,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it has the arrow back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.96,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:33.99,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4CBBC2&\4c&H286EB9&}Batoom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:34.00,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem intends to finish me \Nbecause I touched the arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.87,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Mista, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.04,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Reload, Bullets! Reload the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.54,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a revolver! \NWe need another cartridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.55,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take time to reload it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.19,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.68,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.73,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm throwing it! Catch it, Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.32,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna throw the turtle to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.32,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.30,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Mr. Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.59,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,He's okay. B-But... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:32.64,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Mista, do you remember what \NI said back at the Colosseum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:38.05,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more to Requiem's \Nability that I'm not aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.31,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm starting to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:43.76,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem stopped because \Nthe starting time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.45,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The starting time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.60,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.26,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,It's because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.63,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my body has started to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.04,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it stopped trying to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:59.05,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,This is Requiem's true motive, \Nnow that it's gone berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.23,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to make beings swap souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:07.01,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,meaning the ability that makes them \Nstart to change into something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.74,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,The prelude is over, and the actual \Npiece is now starting to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it gave up on killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:19.04,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,The 4.5-billion-year history of this \Nworld's creatures is starting to change
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.28,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,into something else within a matter of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.36,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,King,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what makes Requiem \Nso truly frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.82,JoJo-internal/narrator,King,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.38,JoJo-internal/narrator,King,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to them, I was able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.29,JoJo-internal/narrator,King,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to understand the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,King,0000,0000,0000,,I'm close to figuring out how to \Nget that arrow from Requiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.67,JoJo-internal/narrator,King,0000,0000,0000,,I'm realizing the method!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.55,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.02,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.35,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,How far has this damn thing spread?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:54.78,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like they're \Ndying or in pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.23,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone just has these vacant stares.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:02.10,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,But there is this fear of \Nbecoming something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:08.32,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,The fear that, slowly but surely, both my \Nbody and my soul are going to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.20,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Trish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.34,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.22,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,The starting time is imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.64,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,It will happen differently for \Neach of us, but it'll start soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.13,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.83,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.05,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff! This is happening \Nbecause you brought the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.61,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,You said it had the power to defeat the boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.46,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,but instead, you basically ended us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:34.90,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! This is far beyond \Nanyone's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.97,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important that we \Nfind a way to defeat Requiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.72,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Good. Get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:47.48,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Get closer to Requiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:53.75,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,If we get closer, I'll be able to fully see \NRequiem's secrets, because I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:58.45,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,The arrow's power will become mine, \Nand the world will grovel at my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.70,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,After it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.41,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.25,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.85,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Trish, Bucciarati! Both of \Nyou stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:05.83,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:06.66,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.23,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you not to move, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:11.60,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,We can catch up to Requiem in a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.93,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Shut up, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.43,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,My body's disappearing already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.26,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up your revolver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:22.23,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,The one that you said broke a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.79,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,This broken part doesn't match up \Ncorrectly with the rest of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:30.44,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If it just broke due to metal fatigue, \Nthey should still fit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:33.40,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at, Giorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.62,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati, I need you to \Nstay right there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.66,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,We need to keep a distance from each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.33,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass! Requiem is getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:45.17,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The Bullets said it was metal \Nfatigue, so it's metal fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.43,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I have a new Beretta, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:51.26,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,The parts aren't matching up \Nbecause a piece flew off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.85,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.34,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,But it could be something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.78,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to tell as soon \Nas we see this lost piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.53,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.61,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave a part of the gun \Nlife and let it loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:10.40,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Moles are basically blind, but their \Nsense of smell is unparalleled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:15.28,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's returned, \Nand it found its lost piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.69,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB4555E&\4c&H9E856F&}Fit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:23.21,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:27.04,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying someone just used \Nimmense force to tear the gun apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:31.10,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! The Bullets and \NI are very clear on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.96,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one who got close \Nto me in this square—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.93,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly right. No one did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.17,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we need to stay \Napart from each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.29,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because his range is only a few meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.66,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.81,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,No one got close to Narancia \Nwhen he was attacked, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.65,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,No one... other than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:58.21,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Polnareff, if your guess is correct \Nand the boss had two personalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:01.08,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,then he should be able to get in \Nand out of another's mind freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:05.09,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Diavolo has inhabited one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:05.76,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:11.28,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If he stays hidden, \NTrish can't detect his existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.20,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,The reason he's staying hidden now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:16.24,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is because he's waiting for us \Nto obtain the arrow for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.70,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he also appeared for a \Nbrief moment to destroy the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.56,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.13,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I know I keep saying this, \Nbut stay away from me, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.10,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his range!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.69,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,My gun was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:35.86,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one closest to the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.07,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.91,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:42.46,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah. When Narancia was attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.61,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The one closest to him was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.75,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. I must do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.26,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem keeps moving farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:00.22,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,This rookie, Giorno Giovanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:03.27,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,He's hiding in one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.52,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,But despite that, we have one advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.03,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Diavolo can make Emperor Crimson appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.52,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he doesn't have complete control \Nof the body he's inhabiting right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.20,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If he had total control
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:22.38,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,of the body he's currently inhabiting, \Nhe wouldn't just stay quietly hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:25.43,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he can't manifest \Nand move around freely
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that we all still live and \Nhaven't been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:31.37,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,In a sense, we have him cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.37,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,It's the turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:37.19,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the closest one to my revolver!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.41,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff is the one who's possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.58,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:43.96,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Polnareff was almost \Nkilled by Requiem earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.55,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,because the boss destroyed the revolver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.02,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,The boss won't let the body he's \Ninhabiting be put in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.33,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.04,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I only sense one being's life force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:59.28,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,This turtle only has one soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.51,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell that, Giorno?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:07.24,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Only if I can get closer \Nand touch their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.74,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.36,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Life force is a mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.46,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If I actually touch someone, \NI can tell how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.42,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:19.36,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to touch each one of you and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:24.13,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,But how are you going to get closer \Nwithin Emperor Crimson's range?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:32.01,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I learned how to detect \NEmperor Crimson from Mr. Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:36.94,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,The moment the droplets suddenly \Nincrease is when time has skipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.02,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.56,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,But whether you can avoid his attack \Nor not will be a matter of luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:47.12,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,as is whether you'll be able \Nto just barely dodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.57,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:58.99,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,When Narancia was killed, \NI was the farthest away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:03.00,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll check you first\Nso we can be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:03.72,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.18,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there! Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.63,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:16.28,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,If Diavolo is actually in you, \Nwhat's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.98,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,When Narancia died, his body was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:25.37,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,My soul was able to travel from \NNarancia's body into my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:26.99,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,but it was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.52,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no chance that he's possessing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.62,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.21,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:40.21,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I have no way of confirming your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.31,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, Giorno,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,do you have a way to definitively \Nconfirm that you only have one soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:49.89,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,You can't check yourself with \Nyour own ability, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.51,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Mista, we can't go after the \Narrow unless we find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.48,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Come any closer and I'll blow your limbs off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:01.92,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:07.28,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Check me first, Giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.95,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.37,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,We're losing more and more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.42,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,depending on how we look at the \Nsituation, we have the boss cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.45,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.00,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.41,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's going to be attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.06,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,If we get closer to one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.23,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD49553&\4c&HC7FFB4&}Slice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.31,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.29,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.19,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.44,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy Lady—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.17,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,No, Trish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.13,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.51,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,He got closer instantly by \Nmoving your body closer to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:12.50,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this \Nmoment, my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:16.05,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you unleashed your Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.98,sign_20643_206_Who_swapped_with,King,0000,0000,0000,,Diagram of swapped souls
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.98,sign_22034_239_Bucciarati,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457.333,143.334)}Bucciarati
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.98,sign_22034_239_Bucciarati,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs6\pos(544,150)}His body has died\N(which means Doppio \Nhas also died)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.98,sign_22034_239_Bucciarati,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(441.334,197.333)}Trish            Mista
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.98,sign_22034_239_Bucciarati,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs6\pos(368.667,265.666)}Diavolo\N(Emperor Crimson\Nhad possessed him)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.98,sign_22034_239_Bucciarati,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(503.334,234)}Giorno
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.98,sign_22034_239_Bucciarati,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(442.667,308.667)}Turtle   Polnareff
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.01,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:32.07,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't revealed your Stand, \NI might've actually been cornered...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.99,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Zipper Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:41.29,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,If I can grab the Stand, \NI can also move the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:45.63,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can at least make this body run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.41,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be attacked! \NBrace yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.83,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to make time leap—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.61,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.97,JoJo-main,Turtle,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.48,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he running without attacking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:01.72,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Through observation, he's already found
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:04.10,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,a way to get the arrow away from Requiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.44,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time! That takes priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.78,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.78,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get there \Nfirst, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.32,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Stop wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.99,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to hesitate \Nbecause that's your own body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:19.26,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.73,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already fired, Bucciarati.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:26.10,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that... I've already fired six shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.49,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,He's running as he makes time leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.88,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,He predicted the course of the bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:46.02,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,After him! If he gets the \Narrow, we're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.40,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,That shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:57.74,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason no one can touch the arrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:01.04,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:06.67,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,When I move, Requiem's shadow moves \Nin the opposite direction from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.78,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,despite the location of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.09,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:16.22,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,To that man, it should look like the \Nshadow is stretching toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:21.11,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,In Bucciarati's eyes, the shadow is \Nstretching in front of Requiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:21.89,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:26.53,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,This shadow is in different \Nplaces depending on the viewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.65,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mystery of Requiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:33.15,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,This is why it can control everyone's souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.71,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,This thing is the shadow of one's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:39.44,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem itself is the shadow of my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:43.75,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,That's why attacking it will \Nmean attacking yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:47.38,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,If we can get rid of this shadow, \NI can get the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.50,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:52.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it has a shadow, then my own \Nlight should be somewhere, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.30,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,He still doesn't have the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.55,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,We're rushing in, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.71,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,The light is behind my own mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:08.40,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,He just destroyed something behind his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.26,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.94,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:17.06,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I, Diavolo, now have the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:23.87,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If Diavolo found a way to grasp the \Narrow, we should take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:30.77,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Because the arm he tore off of me and these \Ndroplets of blood are all just particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.11,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Wind shall now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.93,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.59,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,These ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.41,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.18,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.33,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.64,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.32,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Blast the arrow away from him! \NDon't let him grab it, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.69,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.35,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,They made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:00.79,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite him predicting their \Nmovements, we're still far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:05.04,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,He can only knock the ones coming \Nat him out of their trajectory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.96,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you knock that arrow \Nback and bring it to me, Bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.44,JoJo-main,bull,0000,0000,0000,,H-He'd already thrown...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.04,JoJo-main,bull,0000,0000,0000,,...a civilian into the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:23.04,JoJo-main,Bull,0000,0000,0000,,He figured out the bullets would land \Nand returned the arrow to its place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.00,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,The trash ability of an underling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:31.84,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way your weak mind can \Nsurpass Emperor Crimson's predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.08,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You will not be able to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:36.31,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You're still just trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:38.07,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I will admit though, Bucciarati,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:42.10,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,your team has made me sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:47.61,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,I never dreamed you would be foolish \Nenough to betray the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:51.51,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,nor did I ever think you'd \Nfind out my true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:57.95,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that I've been able to figure \Nout this arrow's true power is a blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:01.93,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gift granted to me by fate \Nbecause I was able to defeat my past!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.82,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I need ammo, Bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.58,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,We told you, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:09.52,JoJo-main,Bullet,0000,0000,0000,,It takes time to reload that cartridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.63,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,We're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.74,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.91,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy... Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:28.29,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't deflect Mista's bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:31.25,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I just made them softer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:36.50,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The bullets stretched out like \Nchewing gum and stuck to your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:40.33,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,and I had them use their elastic force \Nto return and blow through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.22,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Trish... You're still conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.80,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to overcome this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:49.84,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to live in fear \Nand run away from the fate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.39,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that you've passed on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:56.40,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,If it's in my way, I'll just climb over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.11,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The arrow's flying toward me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.89,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the closest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.49,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,He can't get past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:08.20,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he predicts where \Nit'll fall and erases time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.66,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still closer to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.71,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,If only... My daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.61,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,if only you hadn't been born...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:19.89,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Fear truly does come from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:24.78,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You have genuinely angered me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.77,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.01,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H466FD2&\4c&H515278&}Booooom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:39.38,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd overcome this, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:44.38,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You were right, Trish. Now you \Ncan surpass not only the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.02,JoJo-main,King,0000,0000,0000,,but their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:52.37,JoJo-main,Dia,0000,0000,0000,,Trish!
